{"tid":1828841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！美國和平部隊決定撒離中國","createTime":"2020-01-18T08:13:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T11:48:32.000Z","uid":239336,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c8e2747c305b48aaca4fd24acf5b14d86d7e5f1d","tid":1828841,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T08:13:29.000Z","msg":"美國和平隊（Peace Corps）1月16日決定，將終止在中國大陸的志願計劃，2020年6月起，撤出和平隊在華志願人員。 和平隊網站中國項目徵召欄目前顯示：沒有在華和平隊志願者職位。 和平隊已經正式將這一決定通知了國會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 國會參議員馬可&middot;魯比奧1月16日當天發表聲明說，和平隊這一決定，證實了眾所周知的事實，即中國已不再是一個發展中國家，並說，長期以來中國一直假稱 自己是發展中國家，以利用世界銀行和世貿組織等國際機構。<br />\n<br />\n 美國國務卿蓬佩奧星期五受訪​​時談到中國富有狀況時說，除貿易問題外，美國將致力與中國有關的其他問題，例如，在世界各地用大筆金錢，以及通過各種經濟手段，攫取 政治影響。<br />\n<br />\n 眾議院外交委員會共和黨議員邁克爾&middot;麥克考（Michael McCaul）辦公室1月17日新聞稿說，這項決定是遲到的，不過，消息還是令人歡迎，因為和平隊不再需要遵循中共的指示，和平隊 有限資源可以在其他地方得到更好使用。<br />\n<br />\n 這位眾議員還說，和平隊的初衷是幫助有真正需要的發展中國家，而不是支持富國，尤其是美國的&ldquo;戰略敵人&rdquo;。 中國是世界第二大經濟體，斥巨資發展旨在破壞美國國家安全的軍事裝備。 中國違反人權的情況持續擴大，世界對中國的真實面目正在覺醒，美國納稅者的錢不應通過和平隊用在共產黨中國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/amp/us-peace-corp-china-01172020/5250321.html?__twitter_impression=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Famp%2Fus-peace-corp-china-01172020%2F5250321.html%3F__twitter_impression%3Dtrue&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKFLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=ba0d00b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/amp/us-peace-corp-china-01172020/5250321.html?__twitter_impression=true</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b949f0ec5ded52b6e3f02aa7a71097e4d4c6e8","tid":1828841,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T08:15:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"efdc78912d0f804cfcad14c847db7589f10b1d9e","tid":1828841,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T08:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe929032b56f08a50fdca1537c44dc6a68af0a9","tid":1828841,"uid":162008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T08:18:40.000Z","msg":"和平隊係中國有咩做過？  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣就公投完啦 咁香港人呢？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人唔可以再慣性沉默</span></span>，<br />\n一起發聲，習慣投票表達意見吧<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 ~ 一個香港人的投票應用程式<br />\n下載連結：iOS / Android<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKFLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=78848e16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org</a><br />\n<br />\n原post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1821362/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1821362/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"780a9c98634a4f9748eba1bc6e14055744585cce","tid":1828841,"uid":173271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T08:20:17.000Z","msg":"都冇機會對外<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n走都岩Q哂數"},{"pid":"2a03722c73955b142259d8574b6d6c7838a886fb","tid":1828841,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T08:21:24.000Z","msg":"中國正式成為已發展國家，又嬴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c15aa83b390cec9b7828e1bdbb929d03f64ecd","tid":1828841,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T08:21:45.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cla